{"type": "article", "id": 28470, "title": "可折叠座椅包", "description": "", "date": "2016-06-21T06:46:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702152804XCqgK578Le3fFpw9.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>夏天到了，无论是出门远行还是去参加展览，久站数小时都会使人感到疲惫。Brando 推出的这款可折叠座椅背包虽然并不是新鲜的创意（我们之前介绍过 Bago Bago 的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26474.html\">背包椅</a>），但它座椅与背包的分离设计非常巧妙：平时座椅折叠在背包的背垫中，拉开拉链才会释放出支架，背垫也就成为了坐垫，坐起来也会更舒适一些。这是背包的<a href=\"http://lifestyle.brando.com/Foldable-Chair-Backpack_p14415c1774d134.html\">购买链接</a>，售价为 75 美元。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152802eXVWRyusUz6in2PN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152802uTNvFI65BZMUHxez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702152803Sv2JYs3KuL58PA01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}